Text:

1. Musorgsky - Pictures at an Exhibition, "Promenade"
2. "Gnomus"

26. Schoenberg - Pierrot lunaire, No. 8, "Night"
27. No. 18, "The Moonfleck"

35. Ives - The Unanswered Question
36-37. Prokofiev - Alexander Nevsky Cantata, 5, "The Battle on Ice"
38. Japanese kabuki - Dojoji
39. Beijing opera - The Prince Who Changed into a Cat
